Speaking on NBC News' "Meet the Press," Ukrainian President Volodymyr Zelensky made it clear that he would never accept a U.S.-Russia peace deal without Ukraine.
"I will never accept any decision made by the United States and Russia regarding Ukraine, never," Zelensky said. "This is a war in Ukraine, against us, and we are paying with our lives."

content:
Netizen contribution
The "611" overtime study system is a blessing to students at the South Campus of Shangyou Middle School in Shangyou County, Ganzhou City, Jiangxi Province. Now, the third year of high school has only Saturday night off in the second semester.
"For decades, our school has only half a day off every Saturday afternoon from the first year to the third year of high school. The daily study time is from 6:55 in the morning to about 10 o'clock in the evening (adjusted according to the season), up to 15 hours."
Last summer vacation, due to corruption in the education system, the inspection team of the Commission for Discipline Inspection intervened, and each grade briefly enjoyed a double break. However, once the news passed, the third year of high school immediately returned to its original state, and the vacation for the first and second years of high school also changed from half a day to a full day.

name: 李老师不是你老师
content:
From May, the Ministry of Justice of Japan will allow the region name to be marked in the nationality column of the household registration. Previously, in principle, only the country name was allowed to be marked, and people of Taiwanese origin were marked as "China". In the future, the identity of people of regional origin will be taken into consideration. After the revision of the provincial order, those who have been marked as "China" and want to change to "Taiwan" can change it.
Under the current system in Japan, foreigners cannot obtain Japanese household registration even if they marry Japanese. The Japanese government only recognizes household registration for Japanese people and records the name and nationality of the foreign spouse in the marriage information column.
When a foreigner obtains Japanese nationality or becomes an adopted child of a Japanese, he or she can apply for household registration. Record the nationality of origin in the household registration of the person.

fullContent:
英国首相斯塔默星期天说，他已准备好派遣英国军队前往乌克兰，作为战后维和部队的一部分。
 斯塔默在《每日电讯报》上写道，俄乌战争的结束“不能仅是普京再次发动袭击前的暂时停顿”。
 在文章中，斯塔默说，他准备通过“必要时派遣我们自己的军队到地面”为乌克兰的安全保障做出贡献。
 “我不是轻率地说这些，我深感责任重大，因为这可能会让英国军人和女性陷入危险。”
 斯塔默说，英国可以在结束战争的谈判中发挥作用，在乌克兰和平进程中充当欧洲和美国之间的桥梁。
“欧洲和美国必须继续密切合作，我相信英国可以发挥独特作用，帮助实现这一目标。”
他说：“我们正面临一个千载难逢的时刻，关系到我们大陆的集体安全。这不仅是乌克兰未来的问题。这对整个欧洲来说都是生死攸关的问题。”
